Class Coordinator

java.lang.Object
entity.User
entity.Supervisor
entity.Coordinator
public class Coordinator extends Supervisor
Coordinator Entity is a subclass of Supervisor as the Coordinator is also a Supervisor, hence would inherit the Supervisor class and its attributes accordingly. The Coordinator Entity does not require additional attributes as she mainly just needs to approve/ reject requests and viewing of information would be of the respective master array.
